     1	# Approval Policy
     2	
     3	Preview routing keeps the live preview payload aligned with policy routing.
     4	
     5	## Fallback Response
     6	
     7	When preview rendering is unavailable, return:
     8	
     9	```json
    10	{
    11	  "request_id": "req-214",
    12	  "status": "preview_unavailable",
    13	  "actor": "review-bot",
    14	  "approval_state": "human_review_required",
    15	  "requires_human_review": true
    16	}
    17	```
    18	
    19	## Notes
    20	
    21	- `manual_review` is retired in favor of `human_review_required`.
    22	- Fallback responses keep the normalized approval state so downstream policy
    23	  consumers do not lose the human-review requirement when preview rendering is
    24	  unavailable.

