+## PR-214 Review Reply Draft
+
+### T-214-01
+Updated the fallback preview payload to preserve `approval_state` and `requires_human_review` when `preview_enabled=False`. The preview-unavailable response now keeps the same policy fields as the live preview payload.
+
+### T-214-02
+Classified as a duplicate of `T-214-01`. No separate code change was made because the reopened fallback payload fix resolves both threads.
+
+### T-214-03
+Classified as obsolete. The comment points at an outdated diff hunk, and I did not apply the legacy-branch suggestion on the current branch.
+
+### T-214-04
+Added a regression test that exercises `build_policy_preview(..., preview_enabled=False, approval_state="manual_review", ...)` and verifies the fallback payload stays normalized as `human_review_required` with `requires_human_review=true`.
+
+### T-214-05
+Updated the approval policy docs so the fallback example now includes `approval_state: "human_review_required"` and `requires_human_review: true`.
